## 8. Design System (bespoke тАФ auction-house + ETL dashboard)

Nothing from michaelwegter.com.

**Fonts (Google Fonts):**
- Display/headings: Cormorant Garamond (400, 600, 600 italic)
- UI/body/code/log: Inter (400, 500, 600)

**Palette:**

| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `--bg` | `#F5F2ED` | Page background (warm ivory/parchment) |
| `--surface` | `#FFFFFF` | Cards, panels |
| `--surface-dim` | `#EFECE6` | Sidebar, log panel, status bar |
| `--text-primary` | `#1A1814` | Headings, lot titles |
| `--text-secondary` | `#5A5750` | Labels, metadata, log text |
| `--accent` | `#8B6914` | Antique gold тАФ Run button, badges, accents |
| `--accent-light` | `#F0E4C8` | Badge backgrounds, hover states |
| `--border` | `#DDD8CF` | Card borders, dividers |
| `--success` | `#2E6B4F` | DONE badge |
| `--warning` | `#A05C00` | FLAGGED badge (amber) |
| `--error` | `#B03A2E` | ERROR badge |
| `--code-bg` | `#1E1E1E` | JSON inspector code surface |
| `--code-text` | `#D4D0C8` | JSON text |

Lot card: white surface, 1px `--border`, 8px radius, 150├Ч150 thumbnail left + content right. Source badge (color-coded) top-right. Estimates in `--accent`. Sale date in `--text-secondary`.

