## 9. Req тЖТ Feature Traceability Matrix

| Posting Requirement | Demo Feature |
|---|---|
| Python scrapers, multiple sites | 3 Flask scraper modules |
| JS-rendered pages, browser automation | Playwright for Heritage + Bonhams |
| Lighter approach for static pages | `requests`+BS4 for Leland Little |
| Tool judgment (why each tool) | Telemetry log shows tool per source; cover letter Q2 |
| Consistent JSON output + normalization | Normalized schema; JSON inspector |
| Catalog discovery | Catalog-level scrape тЖТ lot enumeration |
| Rate limiting, retries, error logging | SSE events тЖТ telemetry log panel |
| Respectful scraping / flag hardened sites | `flagged_for_api` SSE event (Heritage) |
| Images | Image proxy + card thumbnails + lightbox |
| Per-scraper documentation | Code comments + README in GitHub repo |
| Catalog detection before sale date | `sale_date` field; upcoming auctions prioritized |
| Michael's Python ownership (U.S. Bank) | Cover letter lead + screening Q1 |
| Michael's Playwright/Puppeteer history | Cover letter + screening Q2 (tech stack) |
| Link existing scraper code | New public GitHub repo created by demo-builder |

