## 10. Scope Fences (NOT building)

- No scheduling/cron UI
- No AWS S3/Lambda
- No login to any auction site (public pages only)
- No full-stack framing (proposal explicitly positions as specialist)
- No search-by-keyword (filters + sort is sufficient)
- No data persistence between runs (in-memory per job, cleaned after retrieval)

---

## 11. GitHub Repo

`github.com/michaelwegter` returns 404 тАФ no public profile.

demo-builder must:
1. Create public repo (e.g., `auction-scraper-demo`) via `gh repo create --public` or GitHub API
2. Push: `auction_scraper_blueprint.py`, `auction_scraper_seeds.json`, `README.md` (approach notes), frontend HTML/JS/CSS
3. Return URL to proposal-writer before proposal-writer runs

