## handoff
- produced: Complete build-ready plan тАФ 3 confirmed sources (Leland Little/requests+BS4, Heritage/Playwright+seeded-fallback, Bonhams/Playwright), normalized JSON schema with currency handling, 4 features (SSE stream + JSON inspector with raw JSON-LD toggle + image proxy + telemetry log + filters/export), design tokens (Cormorant Garamond + Inter, ivory/charcoal/antique-gold), full reqтЖТfeature matrix, build sequence
- decisions: Full build (richness 10). Heritage will 403 in prod тАФ `flagged_for_api` + seeded fallback is a demo feature, not a failure. Image proxy required for CDN referrer checks. GitHub repo must be created fresh by demo-builder (no existing public profile). POST /scrape тЖТ GET /stream/<job_id> SSE architecture (not a single streaming GET, which would block).
- next needs: demo-builder: (a) Flask blueprint + 3 scraper modules + SSE endpoint + image proxy, (b) seed 8 Heritage lots in auction_scraper_seeds.json, (c) verify `playwright install chromium` on Surface, (d) vanilla JS frontend, (e) create + push public GitHub repo, (f) register workSamples.js entry
- risks: Heritage live scraping likely always 403 in prod (mitigated by seeded fallback + flagged_for_api UX); Leland Little estimates may all be null pre-auction (acceptable, null with note); Bonhams currency detection must handle GBP/EUR; GitHub repo creation requires `gh` auth token тАФ demo-builder must handle
